 ARRAY['Purpose-built defense division with security clearance infrastructure for classified data programs', 'Project Maven DoD involvement validates the platform for intelligence community AI training data needs', 'Human-in-the-loop annotation with cleared personnel handles data types that offshore labeling cannot', 'Evaluation benchmarks for defense AI ensure model quality before operational deployment'],
 ARRAY['Defense division requires separate onboarding and security qualification from commercial Scale AI products', 'Data labeling at classified levels involves longer timelines and higher costs than commercial annotation', 'Government procurement cycles create significant lead time from program initiation to operational data pipeline', 'Dependence on human annotators at scale creates quality consistency challenges across large labeling programs'],
